&lt;li&gt;Perform topology simulations in the Security Constrained Unit Commitment software and analyze impacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide backup engineering support to the Day-Ahead Market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating activities with internal ISO staff, including Grid Operations, Scheduling, Power System Operations, Market Monitoring, and IT functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform User Acceptance Testing to support market projects and system updates to the Security Constrained Unit Commitment and Real-Time Scheduling programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test and implement network model updates to ensure accurate system representation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform validation to the weather-based load forecasts used in the Day-Ahead and Real-Time market systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Business Management System software deployments by performing BMS parameter validation process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with senior staff members to develop testing and analysis processes and proficiencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
