&lt;li&gt;Master’s Degree (MS) desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No prior industry related or professional experience required; however, six months of experience from a power related internship, co-op assignment or class project desired. This position will be filled at the appropriate level (Associate – Senior) based upon relative experience and qualifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of industry practices regarding power system operations, Unit Commitment, or Economic Dispatch preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
