&lt;li&gt;Assist with representing the NYISO in regulatory proceedings, formal hearings, and &amp;nbsp;rulemakings before administrative agencies and bodies including the FERC, NYPSC, North American Electric Reliability Company, North American Energy Standards Board, Northeast Power Coordinating Council and New York State Reliability Council.&lt;/li&gt;
